\"the setback\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"her sixth Olympic gold\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"her ninth Olympic medal\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"any other U.S. gymnast\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have never had an athlete that close, so it definitely put me on my toes.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"my toes\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it brought out the best athlete in myself,\\\" Biles said of Andrade afterward.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.7250558113122175e-13, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best athlete\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I knew if I did my work, it would all be fine.\\\"\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my work\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles became just the third woman in the history of the Olympics to twice win the individual all-around gold medal, and the first since the 1960s.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"just the third woman\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual all-around gold medal\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1960s\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(The first two-time winner was Larisa Latynina of the Soviet Union, whose nine Olympic golds remain the most ever earned by a gymnast.)\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}, {\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999956981811, \"rank\": 4.290558524102998e-08, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first two-time winner\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"whose nine Olympic golds\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"a gymnast\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Biles, 27, is the first to win her second eight, rather than four, years after her first.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Tokyo Olympics in 2021, Biles withdrew from the individual all-around afterstruggling with the \\\"twisties\\\"and losing the ability to control her body in mid-air.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"twisties\\\"and\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"mid\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The intense pressure hadaffected her mental health, Biles said then, and she ultimately took a two-year hiatus from the sport altogether.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The intense pressure\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-year hiatus\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Leading up to Tokyo, I was so nervous about getting injured physically that I neglected my mental health,\\\" Biles said Thursday.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7910864767951309, \"rank\": 0.2640842727521534, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then I was injured, except it was a mental injury.\\\"\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mental injury\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time, she thought she might never be able to compete in gymnastics again.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But inher return to the sport, she has been dominant, including in this legacy-cementing performance here in Paris.\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2096, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\":